      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EVENTUATE (4) missed the frame last time at Q Parklands but was in the finish the start prior when fifth (34.59) and goes well this course. Better than latest and can atone here. MEPUNGA RULE (3) is a strong stayer well performed over the longer races. Was a strong winner last time (34.22) over 595m at Sandown in a Grade 5. Strike rate this distance strong having won three of four tries. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. One of the key runners again. QUINLEE BALE (1) has a strong record this journey with two wins and a minor from four starts. Scored by 4.5 lengths last time (29.60) in a Grade 4/5 over 515m at Sandown. With even luck and a clean start should be around the money. SHIMA BLUSH (2) has a solid strike rate from this box.",
